<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<!DOCTYPE task PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Task//EN" "task.dtd" []>
<task xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" id="specifying-nbsp-rendering" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="urn:oasis:names:tc:dita:xsd:task.xsd:1.1">
  <title>Specifying NBSP Rendering</title>
  <taskbody id="body">
    <context>
      <p><term>NBSP</term><indexterm>NBSP</indexterm> are non-breaking space symbols that appear in a document to prevent line break at their position. For example, you can see NBSP in <codeph>image</codeph> elements in DITA topics.</p>
      <p>When you open a document  in the WYSIWYG mode,  NBSP are rendered by default as small circles . You can change the view of  NBSP to show them just as spaces.</p>
    </context>
    <steps>
      <step>
        <cmd>Call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <p>To call up the <keyword>Preferences Dialog</keyword>, choose <menucascade>
              <uicontrol>Tools</uicontrol>
              <uicontrol>Preferences</uicontrol>
            </menucascade>.</p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Select the <keyword>Tag Style tab</keyword>.</cmd>
        <info>
          <fig>
            <title>Tag Style tab.</title>
            <image href="preferences-dialog-tag-style-tab-nbsp.png" align="center" placement="break"/>
          </fig>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Set the NBSP option:</cmd>
        <substeps>
          <substep>
            <cmd>To show NBSP as small circles, check the <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Show non-breakable spaces as circles</uicontrol>
              </menucascade> checkbox.</cmd>
          </substep>
          <substep>
            <cmd>To show NBSP as spaces, uncheck the <menucascade>
                <uicontrol>Show non-breakable spaces as circles</uicontrol>
              </menucascade> checkbox.</cmd>
          </substep>
        </substeps>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Apply</uicontrol> button to apply the settings.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Click the <uicontrol>Close</uicontrol> button to close the dialog.</cmd>
      </step>
      <step>
        <cmd>Press <uicontrol>F4</uicontrol> to reload the document.</cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
  <related-links>
    <link href="inserting-nbsp-symbols.xml"/>
  </related-links>
</task>
